task.summary: Hechos el primer voraz y el GRASP.
Started Developing a new Graph class that uses a Matrix object for its representation, so links between nodes can be accessed simply looking at the position defined by the number of the nodes.
First three algorithms are working, and the Graph used has changed from a Graph object (now deprecated) to a GraphMatrix object.
Implemented local search and multi-boot method.
All algorithms working, but still need to check all of them again.
Apparently, every algorithm is working perfectly. Solved a failure that made the program clear every RCL if they were not of the desired size.
Algorithms, by now, are completely finished. Changed the timer of all algorithms for a counter of operations, because the timer was not providing any useful information.
